  test_app (both sent upstream). Require rails 3.2 for testing.

  11 May 2012; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  best_in_place-1.0.6.ebuild:
  Add support for Rails 3.2, Ruby 1.9.

